4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals with no prior knowledge. This 16-week program includes 3 live online classes each week, allowing up to 16 participants to enhance their skills. Students gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, with a focus on cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence analysis. The course also covers risk management and compliance with standards such as ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, participants receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The program is available in English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop